# Supabase Configuration
# Obtain these from your Supabase Dashboard: Project Settings -> API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# ==========================================
# CORS Configuration Requirements
# ==========================================
# Ensure you configure CORS in your Supabase Dashboard:
# 1. Go to Authentication -> URL Configuration
# 2. Add your local development URL (e.g., http://localhost:5173 or http://localhost:3000) to the "Site URL" or "Additional Redirect URLs"
# 3. Add your production domain(s) to the allowed origins.
# Without this, Supabase will reject requests from your frontend.